{
  "stem": "24268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, I-- this lady's sister, Frania-- she was not only the best student from the class, but from the whole school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she used to sing well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she do some drawing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then she looked at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she looked a little bit like you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And anyway, everybody loved her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was about-- my parents friends-- anytime we went, they been all respected by everyone-- Gentile, non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we learned the same way to respond to people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "To us, that's the way we were taught, to respect others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and education, wisdom-- that's what we learn at home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And tradition-- every shabbat-- I mean, my parents were very dedicated to Judaism.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we had also-- my parents also spent a lot-- they fund philanthropic causes for sick people, for they call [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my daddy also-- they married some orphan brides, helped to marry them off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my Daddy also dedicated a part of our apartment, a part which made like a prayer place, which the people came and did their daily prayers, which they call a [NON-ENGLISH] sort of.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my brother, who was very talented, he made the of the ark beautiful two lions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They looked like real.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He painted them and-- which they were holding the Ten Commandments.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, as a teenager-- he was 13 or 14 years old-- for fun, he made a-- a camera.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do you call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A movie projector, which they showed us films, old films, which was so [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we also had a tutor who taught us music.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was singing, [LAUGHS] which they knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in school, I was very active.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was participating in many school plays and recitations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also exercised with the whole school.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
